{
  "logNo": "110171740304",
  "title": "한강공원 삼패지구 피크닉",
  "addDate": "2013. 7. 9.",
  "categoryNo": "42",
  "parentCategoryNo": "1",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=110171740304",
  "html_size": 195544,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110171740304\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110171740304\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:9pt; font-family:'3028548_9';\" class=\"view\"><div style=\"font-size:9pt; font-family:'3028548_9';\" class=\"view\"> \r\n<div align=\"left\"><div>\n<iframe src=\"https://mashup.map.naver.com/view.nhn?mid=bl014103988%40p18174373&type=total\" width=\"402\" height=\"352\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" onerror=\"return true;\" onabort=\"return true;\" style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:8px;background-color:white;\" title=\"포스트에 첨부된 지도\"></iframe>\n</div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>남양주 한강공원 삼패지구. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">&#65279;6월 말의 일요일.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">집에서 처제식구들 만나서 얘기하고 놀다가 늦은시간에서야 집을 나서게 됩니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">비도 올 것 같고해서 안나갈까 하다가,</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">집에만 있자니 너무 답답해서 ^^ 일단 나가고 봅니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">남양주, 양평쪽으로 방향을 잡고 출발!</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">강변북로를 타고 가면서 생각을 합니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">시간이 4시를 넘어가는데, 지금 멀리가면 도대체 몇시에나 집에 오게 되지? </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">그래서 구리를 지나면서 미음나루로 가볼까 하다가 덕소 옆 한강변을 가보기로 합니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">한번도 가보지 않았고, 시설이 어떤지도 모르지만, 그냥 가보기로 ㅎㅎㅎ</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">삼패삼거리를 지나기 직전에 출입로가 있네요. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">와~</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130709_86/isuhani_1373358338027Y4mRF_JPEG/IMG_3429.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130709_86/isuhani_1373358338027Y4mRF_JPEG/IMG_3429.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6BF5890')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130709_86/isuhani_1373358338027Y4mRF_JPEG/IMG_3429.JPG?type=w3\"></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130709_6/isuhani_137335833744552EMc_JPEG/IMG_3321.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130709_6/isuhani_137335833744552EMc_JPEG/IMG_3321.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6BF5890')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130709_6/isuhani_137335833744552EMc_JPEG/IMG_3321.JPG?type=w3\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130709_219/isuhani_1373358337746tqROC_JPEG/IMG_3323.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130709_219/isuhani_1373358337746tqROC_JPEG/IMG_3323.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6BF5890')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130709_219/isuhani_1373358337746tqROC_JPEG/IMG_3323.JPG?type=w3\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">매우 넓습니다. </span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">잔디밭도 참 좋네요. </span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">늦은 시간인지라 많은 사람들이 놀다가 정리하고 떠나는 중이네요.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">그래도&nbsp;여전히 많은 사람들이 그늘막과 텐트, 돗자리 등을 준비하고 피크닉을 즐기고 있더군요.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">위 사진의 동그란 광장에는 분수가 있나봅니다. </span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">낮에는 분수가 나오고 물이 있어서 애들이 놀기 좋나봅니다. </span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">젖은 옷을 갈아입히는 부모들이 많더라구요. </span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130709_16/isuhani_1373358651574ESTFB_JPEG/IMG_3325.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130709_16/isuhani_1373358651574ESTFB_JPEG/IMG_3325.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6BF5890')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130709_16/isuhani_1373358651574ESTFB_JPEG/IMG_3325.JPG?type=w3\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">주섬주섬. </span></span></p>\r\n<p>그늘막을 치고 자리를 잡습니다. </p>\r\n<p>공간이 넓어서 주변에 다른 텐트들과 겹치지 않아서 좋아요.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>딸은. </p>\r\n<p>잔디밭을 맨발로 거닐어봅니다. </p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130709_8/isuhani_1373358651859DuV7y_JPEG/IMG_3339.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130709_8/isuhani_1373358651859DuV7y_JPEG/IMG_3339.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6BF5890')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130709_8/isuhani_1373358651859DuV7y_JPEG/IMG_3339.JPG?type=w3\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>서쪽하늘에는 비구름이 몰려있지만.</p>\r\n<p>이곳 하늘은 화창합니다. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>(해질무렵 비가 조금씩 내렸다 그쳤다 했네요)</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f369296020e5d0c6.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"825\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 1110px\" id=\"20130709_295/isuhani_1373358652017db91N_JPEG/IMG_3349.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6BF5890')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f369296020e5d0c6.jpg\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>일단 나오면 </p>\r\n<p>애들은 즐겁습니다. </p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/27e09a7cbc2f1323.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"825\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 1110px\" id=\"20130709_67/isuhani_1373358652190nqG8M_JPEG/IMG_3358.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6BF5890')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/27e09a7cbc2f1323.jpg\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>요새 부쩍.</p>\r\n<p>아빠와 힘겨루기, 싸우기 놀이가 하고싶어지는 </p>\r\n<p>아들.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130709_104/isuhani_1373358652332JHXHg_JPEG/IMG_3370.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130709_104/isuhani_1373358652332JHXHg_JPEG/IMG_3370.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6BF5890')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130709_104/isuhani_1373358652332JHXHg_JPEG/IMG_3370.JPG?type=w3\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>둘이서 넓은 잔디밭을 마구 달려다닙니다. </p>\r\n<p>달리고.</p><span id=\"husky_bookmark_end_1373358690955\"></span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_start_1373358690955\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_end_1373358692194\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_start_1373358692194\">&#65279;</span> \r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/0a7f64c42dbcce90.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"825\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 1110px\" id=\"20130709_68/isuhani_13733586524987Rl4A_JPEG/IMG_3393.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6BF5890')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/0a7f64c42dbcce90.jpg\"></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">달리고..</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/e99b8335e469ed42.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"825\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 1110px\" id=\"20130709_16/isuhani_1373358652883vszAz_JPEG/IMG_3413.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6BF5890')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/e99b8335e469ed42.jpg\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" />또 달립니다...</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>그래. 체력소비 하고선 오늘은 일찍 잠들거라</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/46eb1e8eac5cb08d.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"825\" style=\"cursor: pointer; BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 740px; rheight: 1110px\" id=\"20130709_5/isuhani_1373358652691PoPBe_JPEG/IMG_3403.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6BF5890')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/46eb1e8eac5cb08d.jpg\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" />트럭에 싣고 다니는 미니 바이킹.</p>\r\n<p>반짝거리는 놀이기구를 보더니</p>\r\n<p>둘이서 태워달라고 난리.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>'무서울텐데?'</p>\r\n<p>\"아니야, 괜찮아!!!\"</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>둘이서만 타라고 했더니 싫답니다. </p>\r\n<p>아빠, 엄마도 같이 탑니다. </p>\r\n<p>(사진 생략 ^^)</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>슬슬 움직일 땐 재밌다고 소리지르고 웃고 난리더니</p>\r\n<p>바이킹이 크게 움직이기 시작하니까 무섭다고 울려고 합니다. </p>\r\n<p>(것봐, 무서울꺼라 했잖아)</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>그래도 내리고선 또 타고 싶다고 하네요 ㅎㄷㄷ<br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130709_172/isuhani_13733586531423lk0o_JPEG/IMG_3439.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130709_172/isuhani_13733586531423lk0o_JPEG/IMG_3439.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6BF5890')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130709_172/isuhani_13733586531423lk0o_JPEG/IMG_3439.JPG?type=w3\"></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">여름이라 해가 길긴 길군요.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">시간이 늦어져도 깜깜해지지 않습니다. </span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">가로등은 다 켜졌네요.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">우리는 슬슬 짐을 챙깁니다. </span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130709_78/isuhani_13733590941924EMkV_JPEG/IMG_3440.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130709_78/isuhani_13733590941924EMkV_JPEG/IMG_3440.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6BF5890')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130709_78/isuhani_13733590941924EMkV_JPEG/IMG_3440.JPG?type=w3\"></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">공원 바로 옆에 보리밥집이 있어서</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">그곳에서 저녁을 먹고 집으로 귀가합니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">남양주공원 삼패지구는</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">넓고, 한적하고, 잔디가 좋습니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">그러나 그늘이 없네요. 매점 혹은 편의점도 없습니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">취사는 당연히 불가능하구요. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">자장면, 치킨 등은 배달해주는 집들이 있더군요.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">간단한 장비로 가볍게 다녀오긴 좋겠네요.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">(그래도 여름 성수기 되면 사람들 많~을 것으로 예상됩니다.)</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p><span id=\"husky_bookmark_end_1373358359102\"></span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_start_1373358359102\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_end_1373358359964\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_start_1373358359964\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_end_1373358365141\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_start_1373358365141\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_end_1373358397037\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_start_1373358397037\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_end_1373358397349\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_start_1373358397349\">&#65279;</span> </div></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
